<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Seth Berkley</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2317?language=en' lang='en'>
The troubling reason why vaccines are made too late ... if they're made at all
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
